{"tid":670363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人啲邏輯真係世界第一","createTime":"2018-05-19T09:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T12:56:43.000Z","uid":143499,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd24b5fe16f65c389f291a4edddf0b14b357402","tid":670363,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"普通腥港人:又要埋怨辛苦，又唔願意改變，唔諗下係邊個一手造成今日問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登時事台: 竟然叫人黃台仰返嚟坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講埋啲大義凜然，公民抗命，犯咗法就要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果司法制度係公平公正咁絕對啱，比著五年前， 最多咪半傷害他人同非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日就算冇片冇證據都可以話梁天琦暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n陪審團俾人影兩次相都可以當冇事發生就知道司法制度有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣同馬來西亞前總理俾人屈雞家冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班閪人叫黃台仰返嚟坐監，你不如叫大陸單維權人士返大陸自首啦， 你不如叫孫中山唔好搞革命唔好逃亡直接向清廷投降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁先係尊重司法制度呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁嘅嘢都講得出，懶係尊重司法制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到自己眾人皆醉唯我獨醒，特登講啲反人性嘅嘢博存在感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外， 前幾日我開咗個post或假如獨立成功後要召開軍事法庭清算班高官同親支人士， 事成後還政於民重新開始一個新嘅民主制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n竟然有人話咁樣做係民粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜有革命唔係以民粹作動力嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果全世界都咁理性完全冇民粹推動，咁唔好話革命呀，示威遊行都冇可能發生喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然過分利用民粹就會變成文化大革命同批鬥大會， 但係一場成功嘅革命絕對唔可以缺乏人民嘅憤怒同民粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n法國大革命有冇民粹成分？<br />\n<br />\n推翻滿清有冇民粹成分？<br />\n<br />\n美國獨立有冇民粹成分？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全部都有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題係人哋真係成功獨立之後革命黨願以下放權力，重新制定新規矩新秩序， 所以先有今日嘅美國同台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人真係政治潔癖，清算又話極右法西斯， 搞少少民粹又話似蘇聯共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好就代價全部由人哋付出，自己坐享其成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最好就等人哋班烈士去坐監，自己就un un腳坐享其成， 繼續喺網上散播&quot;要返工不了&quot; 等待香港獨立，之後自己就可以完全唔使付出任何代價享受自由及改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 我屌曬你哋老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你哋只配做肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></span>"},{"pid":"b70352978b5da2ac0f341d44a1d89288df7f3b48","tid":670363,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"唔好嘥時間問樓主咁巴閉做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家得自己一個衝同自殺冇分別，我哋就係要匯聚力量聚沙成塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該日日喺大學宣傳， 即時唔可以公開咁宣傳都可以喺同學之間分享呢個理念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b3aea37a8794bf92032e0b3481df99c6645f00","tid":670363,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:08:49.000Z","msg":"唔同意同唔滿意就正面回覆，唔好成個懦夫咁"},{"pid":"b12ab45c351cf2247f1d0cd0e45a7ba9678285db","tid":670363,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"講還講<br />\n點解要搬我地豪哥句金句出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109f3895fc0cc2600d29cc594747a19a18e4e2f2","tid":670363,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b12ab45c351cf2247f1d0cd0e45a7ba9678285db","tid":670363,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"講還講<br />\n點解要搬我地豪哥句金句出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d8bea151432107bda50228bc0d9ce4155aa4ac","tid":670363,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"政治潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd13ee3503e24f7fa1d0dd65078241cca1dce82","tid":670363,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42d8bea151432107bda50228bc0d9ce4155aa4ac","tid":670363,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"政治潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:55:54.000Z","msg":"香港人日日想共產黨倒台但係又翹埋雙手唔做嘢，同陳雲作法有乜嘢分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121b5c9335a363fcd727b08aa5c9e8ce8a7228ce","tid":670363,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}